In the Vaadin view GSPs, you can use all of the 
[Grails tags|http://grails.org/doc/latest/guide/theWebLayer.html#tags] as you would in a
normal Grails GSP.

{note}
Sitemesh layout tags are currently not supported. Please use the Vaadin [layout|Tags] tag instead.
{note}

In addition, you can embed Vaadin components in GSPs using the tag library provided by this plugin:

{table}
 *Tag* | *Description*
 *LAYOUTS* |
 [accordion|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [Accordion|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Accordion.html] component to the parent container.
 [horizontalLayout|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [HorizontalLayout|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/HorizontalLayout.html] component to the parent container.
 [layout|Tags] | Adds a 'template-and-content' [GspTemplateLayout|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.GspTemplateLayout] to the parent container.
 [location|Tags] | Adds a 'content-only' [GspLayout|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.GspLayout] component to the location in the parent container.
 [tab|Tags] | Configures a single tab of the parent Vaadin [TabSheet|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TabSheet.html] component.
 [tabs|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [TabSheet|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TabSheet.html] component to the parent container.
 [verticalLayout|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [VerticalLayout|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/VerticalLayout.html] component to the parent container.
 |
 *TABLES* |
 [table|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [Table|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Table.html] component to the parent container.
 [column|Tags] | Configures a single column of the parent Vaadin [Table|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Table.html] component.
 |
 *FORMS* |
 [form|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [Form|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Form.html] component to the parent container.
 [field|Tags] | Configures a single [Field|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/AbstractField.html] of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [checkBox|Tags] | Configures a [CheckBox|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/CheckBox.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [comboBox|Tags] | Configures a [ComboBox|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/ComboBox.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [currencySelect|Tags] | Configures a Currency-populated [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [customField|Tags] | Configures a [DefaultCustomField|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.DefaultCustomField] of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [date|Tags] | Configures a [DateField|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/DateField.html] of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [file|Tags] | Configures a [DefaultUploadField|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.DefaultUploadField] of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [listSelect|Tags] | Configures a [ListSelect|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/ListSelect.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [localeSelect|Tags] | Configures a Locale-populated [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [optionGroup|Tags] | Configures an [OptionGroup|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/OptionGroup.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [password|Tags] | Configures a [PasswordField|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/PasswordField.html] of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [select|Tags] | Configures a [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [text|Tags] | Configures a [TextField|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TextField.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [textArea|Tags] | Configures a [TextArea|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TextArea.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 [timeZoneSelect|Tags] | Configures a TimeZone-populated [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field of the parent Vaadin Form component.
 |
 *MISC* |
 [include|Tags] | Adds a [GrailsIncludeLayout|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.GrailsIncludeLayout] component to the parent container.
 [label|Tags] | Adds a Vaadin [Label|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Label.html] component to the parent container.
 [link|Tags] | Adds a [GrailsButton|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.GrailsButton] component to the parent container.
 [warning|Tags] | Shows a warning-type [Window.Notification|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Window.Notification.html] in the application's main window.
 [error|Tags] | Shows an error-type [Window.Notification|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Window.Notification.html] in the application's main window.
{table}
